An Enum of the different types of states, e.g. intermediate, final states.

2011-11-13

Enum Constant Summary
FINAL
          The final state in the lattice, i.e. that which outputs e.g.  "</s>".
GOAL
          A (potential) goal state in a word label search, i.e. those which have edges outputting a word symbol.
INITIAL
          The initial state in the lattice, i.e.  that which outputs e.g. "<s>".
INTERMEDIATE
          A (potential) intermediate state in a word label search, i.e. those which have edges outputting a non-word symbol.
